x4freetext: Experiment performed at the MP Tandem
accelerator of the Meier-Leibnitz Laboratory of
Ludwig Maximilians University and Technical
University of Munich
130Ba targets with thickness of 100 and 50 mu-g/cm2,
implanted into 30 mu-g/cm2 carbon foil prepared from
BaF2 material 37.61% enriched in 130Ba
Tritons were analyzed with the Q3D magnetic
spectrograph and detected in the focal plane
Focal plane detection system consisted of
three proportional counters and plastic scntillator
counter
Statistical uncertainty
Compiled by S.H.
